      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 23:25:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市收复失地，油价从七个月低点回升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着股市反弹以及利比亚最大油田停产使人们的注意力重新集中在中东地区，油价从七个月低点上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-6</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 23:18:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛认为碳市场将迎来历史性转折点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/goldman-sees-carbon-market-heading-for-historic-tipping-point</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团欧洲、中东和非洲地区自然资源研究主管表示，欧盟向大气中排放二氧化碳的成本将与天然气价格脱钩，这标志着两个市场之间动态的一次历史性转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/goldman-sees-carbon-market-heading-for-historic-tipping-point</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 21:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
